videos.headline: OK State's Mack shows out on both ends of the floor
videos.description: Natasha Mack blocks a shot attempt and lays it in on the other end, as she finishes with 27 points, 15 rebounds and 4 blocks in Oklahoma State's first-round win over Wake Forest.
